    File.ReadAllText(@"C:\TestData\orders.csv"));
```

**Problem:** Depends on an external file at a hard-coded Windows path. This test will fail on any machine that doesn't have `C:\TestData\orders.csv` (every Linux CI agent, every teammate's machine). Also qualifies as **Resource Optimism** â€” no guard that the file exists.

**Fix:** Inline the test data:

```csharp
[TestMethod]
public void ImportOrders_FromCsv_ParsesCorrectly()
{
